<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.3">
<l>uṟikaḷ pōlmeyn narampe ḻuntūṉ taḷarntuḷ ḷameḷki</l>
<l>neṟiyai nōkkik kaṇcu ḻaṉṟu niṉṟu naṭuṅkāmuṉ</l>
<l>aṟiti yākiṉ ṉeñcamaṉ pāyā yiranā mañcolli</l>
<l>veṟikoḷ vaṇṭu paṇkaḷ pāṭum vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before I shudder, halting, [my] eyes rolling [back] toward [my] forehead,</l>
<l>[With] veins bulging out like netting, flesh sagging, and [my] heart failing,</l>
<l>[My] heart, lovingly chanting his one-thousand names, if you know [them],</l>
<l>We will go worship at Badarī, where drunken bees sing melodies.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
